00:00:11,513 --> 00:00:13,694
I'm co-founder of Inkle.

5
00:00:13,694 --> 00:00:16,035
We're an independent studio based here,

6
00:00:16,035 --> 00:00:20,097
not based here, based in Cambridge in the UK.

7
00:00:20,097 --> 00:00:21,938
We specialize in narrative.

8
00:00:21,938 --> 00:00:25,079
So we like to tell good stories.

9
00:00:25,079 --> 00:00:26,400
